                { pattern: "Parallel Structure", example: "You'll know why simple addition fails, how integer programming compresses exponential search spaces, and what Bregman divergence actually means.", exampleZh: "你会知道为什么简单加法会失败、整数规划如何压缩指数级搜索空间、以及布雷格曼散度到底意味着什么。", explanation: "并列结构 why/how/what 三个从句对齐排列，使复杂信息层次分明" }
