            textEn: `<span class="vocab" data-meaning="采用/应用">Adoption</span> is not about price. It's about how many people use <span class="vocab" data-meaning="加密货币">crypto</span> in their daily lives. When your grandmother can send <span class="vocab" data-meaning="跨境的">cross-border</span> payments in seconds without knowing she's using <span class="vocab" data-meaning="区块链">blockchain</span>, that's real adoption.`,
            textZh: `采用率与价格无关。它关乎有多少人在日常生活中使用加密货币。当你的祖母可以在几秒钟内发送跨境支付，而不需要知道她正在使用区块链时，那才是真正的普及。`,
