                { pattern: "When + Present Simple (Conditional)", example: "When your grandmother can send cross-border payments in seconds without knowing she's using blockchain, that's real adoption.", exampleZh: "当你的祖母可以在几秒钟内发送跨境支付，而不需要知道她正在使用区块链时，那才是真正的普及。", explanation: "when 引导条件/时间从句，用一般现在时描述未来可能的场景，使论点更具画面感" }
